short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Admire the beauty of the Audi R8 in a serene night setting with the Audi R8 Parked at Night Live Wallpaper.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
This Chrome extension showcases the iconic luxury sports car, parked under the moonlit sky with a dark, atmospheric backdrop. The high-quality imagery brings out every curve and detail of the Audi R8, creating an elegant, dynamic experience every time you open a new tab.

Features:
🚗 Stunning live wallpaper of the Audi R8 parked under the night sky.
🌐 Customizable search bar to use your preferred search engine.
🕒 Clock and date display to keep you on track.
🔗 Quick-access shortcuts for easy navigation to your favorite websites.
Let the power and style of the Audi R8 enhance your browsing experience, bringing a touch of luxury to every tab you open.
